text: Solana Beach is a city in San Diego County, California, United States. It had a population of 12,802 in 2022. Solana Beach is known for its beaches. The Cedros Design District is located in Solana Beach. It has art shops and boutiques. The weather is comfortable for the whole year. The school districts in Solana Beach are Solana Beach School District and San Dieguito Union High School District. == References == Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in San Diego County, California
title: Solana Beach, California
